<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200922/11977744655b4a31987d029fdf3b2e42.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花鸟《和风鱼涌图》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200922/ecc45483a2b44e23848718ff4938535c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花鸟《平安相伴》</p>
